    "多数同类系统只做流程数字化与被动记录；我们增加了一层情报感知：政策、关税、台风、罢工等会自动关联到您的具体货物并提前预警，而非事后才发现。": "Most systems only digitize and passively record workflows; we add a layer of intelligence sensing — policy, tariffs, typhoons and strikes are auto-linked to your actual cargo and flagged in advance, rather than discovered after the fact.",
