    "不是功能的堆砌，而是你日常工作中每个环节的答案。": "Not a feature checklist — it's the answer to every link in your daily workflow.",
    "不在出问题后救火，而在出问题前预警。自动追踪每个供应商的准时率、质量合格率、价格趋势，恶化前提醒你切换备选。": "Stop firefighting. Automatically track every supplier's on-time rate, quality score, and price trend — get alerted to switch before things go wrong.",
