    "多源备选": "Multi-Source Backup",
    "不再凭感觉判断\"该补货了\"。AI 预测需求 + TCO 全链路比价 + 自动跟单，PO 周期从 3–5 天缩至 1 天内。": "Stop guessing when to reorder. AI demand forecasting + TCO comparison + automated follow-up — PO cycle cut from 3–5 days to under 1 day.",
    "RFQ 询价": "RFQ",
