    "交期预警": "Lead-Time Alerts",
    "库存不是越少越好——断货的代价远大于仓储费。动态安全库存模型帮你找到最优水位，周转天数从 90 天降至 55 天。": "Less inventory isn't always better — a stockout costs far more than warehousing. Dynamic safety stock finds your optimal level, cutting turnover from 90 to 55 days.",
    "智能库位": "Smart Slotting",
