    "FBA 对接": "FBA Sync",
    "订单进来，系统自动选最省最快的方式发出。多渠道接单、智能拆合、SLA 超时预警——不用每天盯屏幕。": "Orders come in, the system auto-picks the cheapest fastest route out. Omni-channel intake, smart split/merge, SLA alerts — no need to stare at a screen all day.",
    "智能路由": "Smart Routing",
