    "HS 智能归类": "AI HS Classification",
    "关税优化": "Duty Optimization",
    "单证 AI 审核": "AI Doc Review",
    "合规预警": "Compliance Alerts",
    "BEYOND THE CORE · 增值模块": "BEYOND THE CORE",
    "供应链跑通了，": "Supply Chain Running Smooth? Next —",
    "把货卖好、把账算清": "Sell Smarter, Know Your Numbers",
    "六大模块管好货的流转，下面这两个帮你把货卖出去、把账算明白。": "The six core modules handle your supply chain flow. These two help you sell smarter and track every dollar.",
    "分销与供销商": "Distribution Network",
    "有好货缺渠道，有渠道缺好货——供销双方还在靠微信对接、手工对账，分账扯皮每周都在发生。品牌方上架分销池，经销商零库存选品，订单完成自动分账。一个人管 100+ 分销商不费力，窜货实时监控。": "Great products but no channels? Channels but no good products? Suppliers and distributors still match over WeChat and reconcile by hand — settlement disputes happen every week. Brands list to a distribution pool; distributors sell stock-free; settlement is automatic. One person manages 100+ distributors effortlessly, with real-time anti-diversion.",
    "供销入驻": "Supplier Onboarding",
    "分销选品": "Product Selection",
    "自动分账": "Auto Settlement",
    "窜货监控": "Anti-Diversion",
    "数据统计与报表中心": "Analytics & Reporting",
    "数据散在采购、仓储、物流各系统，想看经营全貌得等各部门拉 Excel——等报表出来，问题可能已经发生了三天。所有数据汇成一块实时看板，直接打字问\"哪个 SKU 毛利在降？\"，AI 自动定位原因。不等报表，不用开会。": "Data scattered across procurement, warehousing, and logistics — to see the full picture you have to wait for every department to pull Excel files. By the time the report arrives, the problem has been happening for three days. All data unified into one live dashboard. Just type \"which SKU's margin is dropping?\" — AI pinpoints the root cause. No waiting for reports, no meetings.",
    "实时看板": "Live Dashboard",
    "自然语言问数": "Ask-the-Data",
    "成本归集": "Cost Allocation",
    "预警中心": "Alert Center",
    "六个模块，": "Six Modules, ",
    "六套 AI 在背后跑": "Six AI Engines Running Behind Them",
    "AI 不是独立功能包——它长在每个模块的决策节点上。下 PO 时自动比价、库存低了自动预警、航线断了自动推荐备选。你不需要知道 AI 在跑，但它每一秒都在帮你算。": "AI isn't a separate feature pack — it lives inside every module's decision points. Auto-compare quotes when placing POs. Auto-alert when stock runs low. Auto-suggest alternate routes when shipping lanes are blocked. You don't need to know the AI is running — it's doing the math for you, every second.",
    "不是 chatbot，是直接接在业务数据上的 AI。想问\"美西港罢工会影响我哪些货\"——打字就行，秒级出答案。跨采购、物流、关务数据一站式查询，不用翻系统。": "Not a chatbot — AI wired directly into your operational data. Ask \"Which shipments are hit by the port strike?\" — get an answer in seconds. One query across procurement, logistics, and customs. No digging through systems.",
    "需求预测引擎": "Demand Forecasting Engine",
    "不是看去年同期的简单推算。融合历史销量、搜索热度、季节因子、竞品价格等 12+ 维度，按 SKU×区域×周滚动预测，跑在库存消耗前面。": "Not a simple year-over-year extrapolation. 12+ dimensions — historical sales, search trends, seasonality, competitor pricing — rolled up into SKU×region×week forecasts, staying ahead of stock depletion.",
    "风险识别引擎": "Risk Detection Engine",
    "不靠固定阈值——\"交期 > 30 天 = 预警\"太晚了。AI 持续追踪交期、质量、价格的微小波动趋势，在恶化成事故前发出信号，你还有时间切换。": "Not fixed thresholds — \"lead time > 30 days = alert\" is already too late. AI continuously tracks micro-trends in delivery, quality, and pricing, signaling trouble before it becomes a crisis — while you still have time to switch.",
    "TCO 优化引擎": "TCO Optimization Engine",
    "报价看单价，AI 看全局——关税 + 运费 + 仓储 + 资金占用一起算。同一批货走不同路线、不同申报方式，成本可能差 15%，系统帮你揪出来。": "You see unit price — AI sees the full picture: duties + freight + warehousing + working capital, all calculated together. Same goods, different route or declaration method? Total cost can differ by 15%. The system finds it for you.",
    "排程仿真引擎": "Scheduling Simulation Engine",
    "不靠经验猜\"下个月会不会爆仓\"。输入促销计划、航线变化、供应商交期——系统跑完仿真告诉你瓶颈在哪，提前 12 周预演，你还有时间调整。": "Stop guessing \"will the warehouse overflow next month?\" Feed in promo plans, route changes, supplier lead times — the simulation pinpoints where the bottlenecks will be. 12-week preview means you still have time to adjust.",
    "决策推荐卡片": "Decision Recommendation Cards",
    "AI 不只会报警，还会给出 2–3 个可行方案。每个方案要花多少钱、要多久、有什么副作用——你只需要选一个，不用开会讨论。": "AI doesn't just raise alarms — it gives you 2–3 workable options. Each with cost, timeline, and trade-offs spelled out. All you do is pick one. No meetings required.",
    "想看看这些模块如何在您的业务里运转？": "Want to See These Modules Run in Your Business?",
    "预约一次产品演示，我们带您逐模块走一遍真实流程。": "Book a product demo and we'll walk you through each module on real flows.",
    "预约产品演示 →": "Book a Product Demo →",
    "想看这些模块": "Want to See How These Modules",
    "怎么组合到你的业务场景？": "Fit Your Business Scenario?",
    "每个企业的供应链都不一样。去解决方案页，按你的场景对号入座。": "Every supply chain is different. Head to Solutions and find your scenario.",
    "查看解决方案 →": "Explore Solutions →",
