    "CMA CGM、马士基等已把好望角作为亚欧默认航线，单程增加 10–14 天、燃油上升约 30%，每箱附加费 500–1,500 美元。": "CMA CGM, Maersk and others now treat the Cape of Good Hope as the default Asia-Europe route — adding 10–14 days per leg, ~30% more fuel, and $500–1,500 per-box surcharges.",
    "自 2 月底美以空袭伊朗以来，海峡日通行量从约 95 艘骤降至个位数，布伦特原油逼近 95 美元，战争险一度暴涨逾十倍。": "Since the late-February US-Israeli strikes on Iran, daily transits collapsed from ~95 ships to single digits, Brent neared $95, and war-risk premiums spiked more than tenfold.",
    "乌克兰粮食与金属外运走廊安全告急，袭击或推高全球粮价，非洲、中东、亚洲进口国首当其冲。": "Safety on Ukraine's grain and metals export corridor is in jeopardy; the strikes may lift global food prices, hitting importers in Africa, the Middle East and Asia first.",
    "1–5 月乌方打击 15 座炼油厂，约四成俄炼油产能离线，克里米亚燃油配给，俄已限制成品油出口。": "From January to May, Ukraine hit 15 refineries, taking ~40% of Russian refining offline; Crimea is rationing fuel and Russia has curbed product exports.",
    "多家 P&I 俱乐部 72 小时内取消海湾战争险承保，西方船舶保费升至船价数个百分点，成本沿全链路传导。": "Several P&I clubs canceled Gulf war-risk cover within 72 hours; premiums for Western-flagged ships rose to several percent of hull value, cascading down the chain.",
    "过境俄罗斯—白俄罗斯—波兰的主通道持续受地缘冲突影响，陆运时效与成本上升，企业转向多枢纽与备选路由。": "The main corridor via Russia–Belarus–Poland remains hit by geopolitical conflict; land transit times and costs are rising, pushing firms toward multi-hub and backup routes.",
    "4 月 6 日起钢、铝、铜及衍生品按全额征税：主金属 50%、衍生品 25%、部分工业设备 15%，重塑采购成本与产地选择。": "From April 6, steel, aluminum, copper and derivatives are taxed on full value — 50% primary, 25% derivatives, 15% on some industrial equipment — reshaping cost and sourcing.",
    "国际贸易法院裁定 Section 122 关税违法，但联邦巡回法院发出临时中止令，CBP 继续照常征收，退税并不自动。": "The Court of International Trade ruled the Section 122 tariff unlawful, but a Federal Circuit stay keeps it in force; CBP keeps collecting and refunds are not automatic.",
    "2025 年 4 月七类中重稀土许可制仍生效；10 月扩大管制暂停至 11 月 10 日，若重启，域外条款将波及含中国稀土的海外制成品。": "The April 2025 licensing regime on seven heavy rare earths still applies; the October expansion is suspended until November 10 — if revived, extraterritorial rules would hit overseas goods containing Chinese rare earths.",
    "商务部澄清：对总部在华企业，其海外子公司同样受 AI 芯片出口限制约束；H200 按个案审查，Blackwell 仍禁运。": "Commerce clarified that AI-chip limits apply to overseas subsidiaries of China-headquartered firms; the H200 is reviewed case-by-case while Blackwell remains banned.",
    "自 1 月 1 日起，钢铁、水泥、铝、化肥、电力、氢进口需具备授权申报人资格并清缴碳证；Q1 碳价 75.36 欧元/吨。": "From January 1, imports of steel, cement, aluminum, fertilizer, electricity and hydrogen require authorized-declarant status and certificate surrender; the Q1 carbon price is €75.36/t.",
    "运河管理局称年内维持 38 班/日、不限航；但 El Niño 强度上升，2027 旱季或重演 2023 减班至 22 班/日的局面。": "The canal authority will keep 38 transits/day with no restrictions this year; but a strengthening El Niño could replay 2023's cut to 22/day in the 2027 dry season.",

