    "模块化设计，先从一个场景切入，数周内看到效果再扩展。不是动辄 12 个月的笨重部署。": "Modular design. Start with one scenario, see results in weeks, then expand. Not a 12-month deployment.",
    "批量入境内保税仓，下单后清关发货。1–3 天妥投，单件物流成本比直邮低 30–40%。": "Bulk into bonded warehouse, ship per order. 1-3 day delivery at 30-40% lower cost than direct mail.",
    "FBA 保 Prime 时效 + 海外仓压成本，双仓并行，AI 需求预测驱动补货节奏。": "FBA for Prime speed + overseas warehouse for cost, with AI forecasting driving replenishment.",
    "下 PO 自动比价，库存低了自动预警，航线断了自动推荐备选——AI 长在每个决策节点上。": "Auto-compare at PO, auto-alert low stock, auto-suggest alternate routes, AI at every decision point.",
    "多源采购 + 多枢纽物流 + 弹性路由。单点断供数小时内重组链路，不把鸡蛋放在一个篮子里。": "Multi-source + multi-hub + elastic routing. Rebuild the chain within hours of a break.",
    "直接对接业务数据库，用自然语言提问。问\"美西港罢工会影响我哪些货\"，秒级给出受影响清单与建议。": "Wired into your database. Ask which shipments are hit? Get the impacted list and plan in seconds.",
